 ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我七岁那年，妈妈告诉我</span></p><p begin="24.854" end="28.256" itunes:key="L2" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="24.854" end="24.985">&quot;Go</span> <span begin="25.345" end="25.627">make</span> <span begin="25.627" end="26.063">yourself</span> <span begin="26.063" end="26.379">some</span> <span begin="26.379" end="26.732">friends,</span> <span begin="26.732" end="26.850">or</span> <span begin="26.850" end="27.178">you&apos;ll</span> <span begin="27.178" end="27.393">be</span> <span begin="27.393" end="28.256">lonely&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“去交些朋友，否则你会孤单寂寞”</span></p><p begin="28.357" end="30.701" itunes:key="L3" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="28.357" end="28.840">Once,</span> <span begin="28.840" end="29.178">I</span> <span begin="29.178" end="29.255">was</span> <span begin="29.255" end="29.972">seven</span> <span begin="29.972" end="30.309">years</span> <span begin="30.309" end="30.701">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我七岁那年</span></p><p begin="36.662" end="40.417" itunes:key="L4" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="36.662" end="36.841">It</span> <span begin="36.841" end="37.171">was</span> <span begin="37.171" end="37.422">a</span> <span begin="37.422" end="37.794">big-</span><span begin="37.794" end="38.202">big</span> <span begin="38.202" end="38.652">world,</span> <span begin="38.652" end="38.867">but</span> <span begin="38.867" end="39.143">we</span> <span begin="39.143" end="39.390">thought</span> <span begin="39.390" end="39.649">we</span> <span begin="39.649" end="39.909">were</span> <span begin="39.909" end="40.417">bigger</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">世界很大很大，但我们自以为更强大</span></p><p begin="40.870" end="44.485" itunes:key="L5" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="40.870" end="41.231">Pushing</span> <span begin="41.231" end="41.435">each</span> <span begin="41.435" end="41.851">other</span> <span begin="41.851" end="42.212">to</span> <span begin="42.212" end="42.418">the</span> <span begin="42.418" end="42.903">limits,</span> <span begin="42.903" end="43.198">we</span> <span begin="43.198" end="43.404">were</span> <span begin="43.404" end="43.902">learning</span> <span begin="43.902" end="44.485">quicker</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">彼此激励挑战极限，我们学得更快</span></p><p begin="44.916" end="48.440" itunes:key="L6" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="44.916" end="45.148">By</span> <span begin="45.148" end="45.777">11,</span> <span begin="45.777" end="46.393">smoking</span> <span begin="46.393" end="46.694">herb</span> <span begin="46.694" end="46.850">and</span> <span begin="46.850" end="47.379">drinking</span> <span begin="47.379" end="47.936">burning</span> <span begin="47.936" end="48.440">liquor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">十一岁时，抽着大麻，喝着烈酒</span></p><p begin="48.894" end="52.334" itunes:key="L7" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="48.894" end="49.322">Never</span> <span begin="49.322" end="49.662">rich,</span> <span begin="49.662" end="49.873">so</span> <span begin="49.873" end="50.130">we</span> <span begin="50.130" end="50.369">were</span> <span begin="50.369" end="50.612">out</span> <span begin="50.612" end="50.869">to</span> <span begin="50.869" end="51.121">make</span> <span begin="51.121" end="51.270">that</span> <span begin="51.270" end="51.906">steady</span> <span begin="51.906" end="52.334">figure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">从不富裕，所以我们立志要挣大钱</span></p><p begin="52.393" end="56.780" itunes:key="L8" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="52.393" end="52.734">Once,</span> <span begin="52.734" end="52.912">I</span> <span begin="52.912" end="53.314">was</span> <span begin="53.314" end="53.926">11</span> <span begin="53.926" end="54.369">years</span> <span begin="54.369" end="54.589">old,</span> <span begin="54.902" end="55.020">my</span> <span begin="55.383" end="55.884">daddy</span> <span begin="55.884" end="56.393">told</span> <span begin="56.393" end="56.780">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我十一岁那年，爸爸告诉我</span></p><p begin="56.835" end="1:00.281" itunes:key="L9" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="56.835" end="57.095">&quot;Go</span> <span begin="57.388" end="57.608">get</span> <span begin="57.608" end="58.220">yourself</span> <span begin="58.220" end="58.371">a</span> <span begin="58.371" end="58.729">wife,</span> <span begin="58.729" end="58.816">or</span> <span begin="58.816" end="59.191">you&apos;ll</span> <span begin="59.191" end="59.377">be</span> <span begin="59.377" end="1:00.281">lonely&quot;</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">“去找个妻子，否则你会孤单寂寞”</span></p><p begin="1:00.359" end="1:02.643" itunes:key="L10" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:00.359" end="1:00.704">Once,</span> <span begin="1:00.704" end="1:00.919">I</span> <span begin="1:00.919" end="1:01.384">was</span> <span begin="1:01.384" end="1:01.946">11</span> <span begin="1:01.946" end="1:02.372">years</span> <span begin="1:02.372" end="1:02.643">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我十一岁那年</span></p><p begin="1:08.696" end="1:12.447" itunes:key="L11" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:08.696" end="1:08.874">I</span> <span begin="1:08.874" end="1:09.443">always</span> <span begin="1:09.443" end="1:09.830">had</span> <span begin="1:09.830" end="1:10.193">that</span> <span begin="1:10.193" end="1:10.496">dream</span> <span begin="1:10.496" end="1:11.179">like</span> <span begin="1:11.179" end="1:11.354">my</span> <span begin="1:11.354" end="1:11.679">daddy</span> <span begin="1:11.679" end="1:12.216">before</span> <span begin="1:12.216" end="1:12.447">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我总怀揣着和父亲一样的梦想</span></p><p begin="1:12.626" end="1:16.487" itunes:key="L12" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:12.626" end="1:13.161">So</span> <span begin="1:13.161" end="1:13.257">I</span> <span begin="1:13.257" end="1:13.868">started</span> <span begin="1:13.868" end="1:14.281">writing</span> <span begin="1:14.281" end="1:14.716">songs,</span> <span begin="1:14.716" end="1:14.791">I</span> <span begin="1:14.791" end="1:15.345">started</span> <span begin="1:15.345" end="1:15.783">writing</span> <span begin="1:15.783" end="1:16.487">stories</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">于是我开始了写歌，开始了写故事</span></p><p begin="1:16.624" end="1:20.442" itunes:key="L13" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:16.624" end="1:17.185">Something</span> <span begin="1:17.185" end="1:17.703">about</span> <span begin="1:17.703" end="1:17.923">the</span> <span begin="1:17.923" end="1:18.653">glory</span> <span begin="1:18.653" end="1:18.875">just</span> <span begin="1:18.875" end="1:19.333">always</span> <span begin="1:19.333" end="1:19.681">seemed</span> <span begin="1:19.681" end="1:19.883">to</span> <span begin="1:19.883" end="1:20.204">bore</span> <span begin="1:20.204" end="1:20.442">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">那些所谓的荣耀总让我觉得无趣</span></p><p begin="1:20.666" end="1:24.345" itunes:key="L14" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:20.666" end="1:20.932">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:20.932" end="1:21.357">only</span> <span begin="1:21.357" end="1:21.709">those</span> <span begin="1:21.709" end="1:21.851">I</span> <span begin="1:21.851" end="1:22.324">really</span> <span begin="1:22.324" end="1:22.680">love</span> <span begin="1:22.680" end="1:22.917">will</span> <span begin="1:22.917" end="1:23.364">ever</span> <span begin="1:23.364" end="1:23.883">really</span> <span begin="1:23.883" end="1:24.184">know</span> <span begin="1:24.184" end="1:24.345">me</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为只有我真正爱的人才能真正了解我</span></p><p begin="1:24.382" end="1:28.591" itunes:key="L15" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:24.382" end="1:24.873">Once,</span> <span begin="1:24.873" end="1:25.172">I</span> <span begin="1:25.172" end="1:25.358">was</span> <span begin="1:25.358" end="1:25.927">20</span> <span begin="1:25.927" end="1:26.360">years</span> <span begin="1:26.360" end="1:26.862">old,</span> <span begin="1:26.862" end="1:27.266">my</span> <span begin="1:27.266" end="1:27.846">story</span> <span begin="1:27.846" end="1:28.329">got</span> <span begin="1:28.329" end="1:28.591">told</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年，我的故事被传唱</span></p><p begin="1:29.169" end="1:32.280" itunes:key="L16" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:29.169" end="1:29.682">Before</span> <span begin="1:29.682" end="1:29.887">the</span> <span begin="1:29.887" end="1:30.326">morning</span> <span begin="1:30.326" end="1:30.669">sun,</span> <span begin="1:30.669" end="1:30.868">when</span> <span begin="1:30.868" end="1:31.263">life</span> <span begin="1:31.263" end="1:31.455">was</span> <span begin="1:31.455" end="1:32.280">lonely</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在清晨的太阳升起之前，生活曾那么孤单</span></p><p begin="1:32.363" end="1:37.146" itunes:key="L17" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:32.363" end="1:32.903">Once,</span> <span begin="1:32.903" end="1:33.197">I</span> <span begin="1:33.197" end="1:33.366">was</span> <span begin="1:33.366" end="1:33.884">20</span> <span begin="1:33.884" end="1:34.332">years</span> <span begin="1:34.332" end="1:35.280">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="1:35.744" end="1:37.146"><span begin="1:35.744" end="1:36.211">(Lukas</span> <span begin="1:36.211" end="1:37.146">Graham!)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">卢卡斯·格雷厄姆！</span></span></p><p begin="1:40.715" end="1:44.530" itunes:key="L18" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:40.715" end="1:40.876">I</span> <span begin="1:40.876" end="1:41.302">only</span> <span begin="1:41.302" end="1:41.820">see</span> <span begin="1:41.820" end="1:42.163">my</span> <span begin="1:42.163" end="1:42.620">goals,</span> <span begin="1:42.620" end="1:42.870">I</span> <span begin="1:42.870" end="1:43.143">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:43.194" end="1:43.711">believe</span> <span begin="1:43.711" end="1:43.958">in</span> <span begin="1:43.958" end="1:44.530">failure</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我只看到我的目标，我不相信失败</span></p><p begin="1:44.691" end="1:48.338" itunes:key="L19" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:44.691" end="1:45.207">&apos;Cause</span> <span begin="1:45.207" end="1:45.368">I</span> <span begin="1:45.368" end="1:45.698">know</span> <span begin="1:45.698" end="1:45.775">the</span> <span begin="1:45.775" end="1:46.363">smallest</span> <span begin="1:46.363" end="1:46.928">voices,</span> <span begin="1:46.928" end="1:47.184">they</span> <span begin="1:47.184" end="1:47.363">can</span> <span begin="1:47.363" end="1:47.703">make</span> <span begin="1:47.703" end="1:47.873">it</span> <span begin="1:47.873" end="1:48.338">major</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我知道最微小的声音也能成就大事</span></p><p begin="1:48.696" end="1:52.486" itunes:key="L20" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:48.696" end="1:48.873">I</span> <span begin="1:48.873" end="1:49.107">got</span> <span begin="1:49.107" end="1:49.348">my</span> <span begin="1:49.348" end="1:49.873">boys</span> <span begin="1:49.873" end="1:50.136">with</span> <span begin="1:50.136" end="1:50.349">me,</span> <span begin="1:50.689" end="1:50.859">at</span> <span begin="1:50.859" end="1:51.350">least</span> <span begin="1:51.350" end="1:51.709">those</span> <span begin="1:51.709" end="1:51.873">in</span> <span begin="1:51.873" end="1:52.486">favor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我有我的兄弟们陪着我，至少是那些支持我的</span></p><p begin="1:52.701" end="1:56.357" itunes:key="L21" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="1:52.701" end="1:52.879">And</span> <span begin="1:52.879" end="1:53.044">if</span> <span begin="1:53.044" end="1:53.159">we</span> <span begin="1:53.159" end="1:53.304">don&apos;t</span> <span begin="1:53.304" end="1:53.713">meet</span> <span begin="1:53.713" end="1:54.161">before</span> <span begin="1:54.161" end="1:54.354">I</span> <span begin="1:54.354" end="1:54.680">leave,</span> <