:lang="zh-CN">曾几何时，我二十岁那年</span></p><p begin="2:12.272" end="2:16.667" itunes:key="L25" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:12.272" end="2:12.869">Soon,</span> <span begin="2:12.869" end="2:13.176">we&apos;ll</span> <span begin="2:13.176" end="2:13.357">be</span> <span begin="2:13.357" end="2:13.902">30</span> <span begin="2:13.902" end="2:14.344">years</span> <span begin="2:14.344" end="2:14.846">old,</span> <span begin="2:14.846" end="2:15.257">our</span> <span begin="2:15.257" end="2:15.733">songs</span> <span begin="2:15.733" end="2:15.897">have</span> <span begin="2:15.897" end="2:16.236">been</span> <span begin="2:16.236" end="2:16.667">sold</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我们将到三十岁，我们的歌已被传唱</span></p><p begin="2:16.871" end="2:20.065" itunes:key="L26" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:16.871" end="2:17.333">We&apos;ve</span> <span begin="2:17.333" end="2:17.783">traveled</span> <span begin="2:17.783" end="2:18.222">around</span> <span begin="2:18.222" end="2:18.418">the</span> <span begin="2:18.418" end="2:18.741">world,</span> <span begin="2:18.741" end="2:18.917">and</span> <span begin="2:18.917" end="2:19.079">we&apos;re</span> <span begin="2:19.079" end="2:19.500">still</span> <span begin="2:19.500" end="2:20.065">roaming</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们环游世界，仍在四处漂泊</span></p><p begin="2:20.284" end="2:22.691" itunes:key="L27" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:20.284" end="2:20.866">Soon,</span> <span begin="2:20.866" end="2:21.172">we&apos;ll</span> <span begin="2:21.172" end="2:21.285">be</span> <span begin="2:21.285" end="2:21.937">30</span> <span begin="2:21.937" end="2:22.342">years</span> <span begin="2:22.342" end="2:22.691">old</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不久，我们将到三十岁</span></p><p begin="2:28.652" end="2:32.570" itunes:key="L28" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="2:28.652" end="2:28.765">I&apos;m</span> <span begin="2:28.765" end="2:29.376">still</span> <span begin="2:29.376" end="2:29.763">learning